article_title: How to Trade 5 Health Insurance Companies
article_text:
Jim Cramer's 'Mad Money' Recap: These Stocks Still Sweet Despite Sour Market

There are lots of stocks still working in this market, and Cramer tells you which ones.

article_metadata.description: Here's how to use technical charts to trade health insurance companies Aetna (AET), Anthem (ANTM), Cigna (CI), Centene (CNC) and UnitedHealth (UNH).
article_metadata.author: Richard Suttmeier
